<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Large <rs type="material">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">block</rs> without moulding (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.815</measure>  × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.61</measure>  × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.59</measure>), with right side and bottom edge surviving; an adjoining fragment to the left was seen in 1967. There are <seg cert="low">clamp holes</seg> from later use on the face.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on the face.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>Hellenistic; l.1, <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.055-0.065</measure>; l.2, <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.05-0.08</measure></p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
<date cert="low" exact="none" notAfter="-0001" notBefore="-0300">Hellenistic</date> (<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>)
</p>
</div>
